title: ABB SA/S12.16.6.1

generalInformation.catalogDescription: SA/S12.16.6.1 Switch Actuator, 12-fold, 16/20 AX, C-Load, Current Det, MDRC
generalInformation.longDescription: Uses potential free contacts to switch 12 independent electrical loads via the ABB i-bus®. Each output has an independent load current detection.
